name 'computer-systems-postassessment-intro_v2-2025'
title 'Computer Systems and Devices Pre-Assessment'
markdown <<MARKDOWN
Now that you’ve completed the unit, this assessment will measure your understanding of computer components, troubleshooting, data in computing, AI applications, and ethical considerations in emerging technologies.

- Read each question carefully and **apply what you've learned** to choose the best answer.
- Some questions involve **real-world scenarios**! Think critically about how computers function and impact our world.
- This assessment is an opportunity to **show your growth**, so take your time and do your best!
MARKDOWN
